title: Mysterious Ways
description:
'Mysterious Ways'

Top Cow Productions/Image Comics, 2012, 160 pages

Written by Jason Rubin

Pencils by Tyler Kirkham

Inks by Sal Regla

Colors by Arif Prianto

THIS KILLER JUST SAVED YOUR LIFE! Sam, an alcoholic convicted ex-cop, wakes up with a mysterious piece of silver in his hand and soon finds himself the prime suspect in a serial murder case pursued by a relentless, picture-perfect FBI agent. But in this story of stereotypes, nothing is what it seems...
